# Architecture (IS_01)

| Layer | Path | Stack |
|--------|------|--------|
| Web | `apps/web` | Next.js 14 App Router, React 18, Tailwind, Zustand |
| API | `apps/api` | NestJS 10, Prisma, PostgreSQL |
| Domain | `packages/is-domain` | Shared TS types/build output → `dist/` |
| AI (Phase 2) | `apps/ai` | FastAPI (stub / future) |
| Twenty CRM | `twenty/` | Submodule / upstream app; own `.cursor` rules |

**Monorepo root**: `package.json` scripts orchestrate `preflight`, `dev:web`, `dev:api`, `start:dev`, DB scripts. **No root `src/`** — app code lives under `apps/*` and `packages/*`.

**Docs**: `README.md`, `ARCHITECTURE.md`, `docs/GLOSSARY.md`, `AGENTS.md` (MVP priority).
